                            {paymentIntentDetails.receipt_email} for a receipt,
                            and <Link href="/contact">contact us</Link> if you
                            have any questions. Once again, we appreciate your
                            support!
                        </p>
                        {/* Display other relevant details here */}
                    </div>
                )}
                <Link
